nodes.text: A Sullustan male served the Alliance to Restore the Republic as a technician during the Galactic Civil War. In 4 ABY,[source?] the technician was tasked with extracting a code from a ID10 seeker droid utilized by Commander Iden Versio of the Galactic Empire's Inferno Squad. While Versio was held captive by the captain of the Invincible Faith, the Sullustan attempted to extract the code, but the droid was reactivated by Version from her cell and shocked the technician, electrocuting him in the process. One of the Rebel guards which the droid found on his way to Versio later shared the technician's fate.
This Sullustan Rebel technician appeared in Star Wars Battlefront II.
